    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 UART implementation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Design:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Accepts a CubeMX-configured UART_HandleTypeDef*.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Blocking TX via HAL_UART_Transmit.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Blocking RX via HAL_UART_Receive.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Optional software circular RX buffer fed by idle-line DMA.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Printf via vsnprintf + Write. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
